quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"Chisimu Uwwe tujitulwisye jalakwe (Qur'aniji) m’Chilo Chakuchimbichika."
  97,2,"Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Chilo Chakuchimbichika?"
  97,3,"Chilo Chakuchimbichikachi chiŵele chambone nnope kupunda myesi jakwana sausande (1000). ",footnotes:1:Myesi sausande ikwana yaka 83 ni myesi 4.
  97,4,"Achimalaika akasatulukaga pamo ni Nsimu (Jibulilu) mu Chele (Chilochi) kwa lisosa lya M’mbuje gwao, kwisa kulondesya chindu chilichose (pakuchiŵika mu mpango wakwe). ",footnotes:1:“Mu chele (chilochi) chikasaŵichidwaga m’mangwakwe chindu chilichose chalunda lwakusokoka.” (44:4) Ichindu yalunda lwakusokoka yakwe mpela: kupagwa kwa ŵandu kwisa soni iwumbe yakulekanganalekangana, kuwa kwao, kupedwa malisiki, kupedwa makungu ni ine yosope yakwapata achiiwumbe mu chaka chosope chachikwika, mpela muŵapanjiile Allah kalakala.
  97,5,"Ntunjelele-tunjelelepe! Chele Chilocho, mpaka kumasikusiku. ",footnotes:1:Akusimulila Ȃishah رضي الله عنهم yanti: Ntenga jwa Allah ﷺ jwatite: “N’jisosejesoseje Lailatul Qadr mu ilo ya chiŵalanjilo changakomboleka gaŵa ni 2 ni ngasigala kakusigala (mpela ilo ya 21, 23, 25, 27 ni 29), mu ilo likumi yambesi yamwesi wa Ramadhan.” (Swahîh Al-Bukhârî, Hadith No. 1913.
  98,1,"Ŵandu achimakafili kutandila achinsyene chitabu (Ayuda ni Akilisito) kwisa soni ŵakuwanganya (Allah ni isanamu), nganaŵa alekangene (ni ukafili wao) kwikanila ndema ja chayichilile chilosyo chakuonechela palangulangu."
  98,2,"(Jwali) Ntenga (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwakuumila kwa Allah jwaakusooma (Qur’an jajili mu) ikalakala yakuswejesyedwa."
  98,3,"Mwalakwemo mwana malamusi gagoloka."
  98,4,"Chisimu Allah akupeleka chanasa kwa Ntume (Muhammadi ﷺ), nombe nao soni Achimalaika (akum’bombelaga chanasa Ntumejo ﷺ). E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Mum’bombelani chanasa jwalakwe ni kum’bombela soni ntendele."
  98,5,"Ni nganalamulidwa ikaŵeje yanti an'galagatileje Allah mwakunswejechesya dini Jakwe pakupendechela ku Uujika Wakwe (nikutalikangana nayo isanamu), nikuti ajimicheje Swala mwakolosya ni kutolaga Zaka, soni jalakwejo ni dini jagoloka."
  98,6,"Chisimu ŵandu ŵaakanile (dini ja Usilamu); kutandila achinsyene chitabu (Ayuda ni Akilisito) kwisa soni ŵakuwanganya (Allah ni isanamu), chakaŵe m’moto wa Jahannama, chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo. Ŵanganyao ni iŵumbe yakusakala nnope. ",footnotes:1:Nnole chilaaki cha Ȃya ja (3:85), nambo soni Ȃya ja (4:47) ni chilaaki chakwe.
  98,7,"Chisimu ŵandu ŵaakulupilile nikutendaga yambone, ŵanganyao ni iwumbe yambone nnope."